P.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

Q.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
Q.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

P_and_Q.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025 AND will I eat a blueberry tomorrow?
P_and_Q.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025 AND I eat a blueberry tomorrow. Resolves NO otherwise.
